## Support for direct GeoJSON

Python:

``` python
import IPython
import json

def geojson(data):
  bundle = {}
  bundle['application/vnd.geo+json'] = data
  IPython.display.display(bundle, raw=True)

import requests
coffee = requests.get("https://bit.ly/coffeeDC").json()

geojson(coffee)
```

